sql:
SELECT AVG(metric_value) AS average_metric_value
FROM committee_metrics
WHERE metric_type = 'Quantitative';

SELECT file_size, description
FROM attachments
ORDER BY file_size DESC;

external_knowledge:
Active committee chairpersons are those who are currently leading a committee with a status of 'Active'; 
Approved goals are those with a status of 'Approved' in the goals table; 
Upcoming meetings are those scheduled for a future date;
Goals in progress are those with a latest report date available; 
Received notification refers to those with a notification status of 'Sent'; 
Completed milestones are those with a status of 'Completed'.

sql:
SELECT metric_value
FROM committee_metrics
WHERE committee_id = 0 AND metric_name = 'Goals Achieved';

SELECT deliverable_status, COUNT(*)
FROM deliverables
GROUP BY deliverable_status;
